okay so this is aa cartoon

but he misses
so he’s thinking
okay how am I gonna get this roadrunner
soo hee goes to a cliff
aand he sees that down below is the roadrunner’s path
sso he gets an anvil
and he thinks that
when the roadrunner passes by
he’ll throw the anvil on the roadrunner
and he’llbe dead or whatever
and so um
so he also attaches a rope to the cliff that he’s on
and then there’s a cliff on the other side
of the roadrunner’s path ?
so attaches the rope to the other side of the cliff
and then he starts to walk across the rope
holding the anvil
and since the anvil is so heavy
it brings him down
the rope stretches ? pretty much to the ground ?
and when the roadrunner comes by
the coyote isn’t fast enough
to throw the anvil on the roadrunner ?
so the roadrunner just like he comes up to the coyote

’cause he’s so fast

the coyote who’s still on the rope
he got shot up into the air

aand um it’s supposed to be uh
a parachute ?

and then it ends

and the coyote takes the lower path

to see where he is

and then it explodes
and then the last like picture on the screen it says YIPES
